reviews.text: Delicious food and good service. Nice boss always talks to customers.

I have been there for three times now! 

First time for dinner, second time for lunch, third time for tea time :)

The standard is consistent, service is good! They are run by family! Not much restaurant was run by family in Hong Kong! 

Must try their Liquor-Saturated Chicken and Pork Knuckle. No service charge during weekdays :)

Very good food with affordable price, around 40 for lunch and 60 for dinner. I prefer it over certain franchised restaurants that serve similar food. One of the very few decent restaurants in ma on shan.
Good food.
Good for a quick and nice noodle lunch. The noodle has good tasty sesame sauce taste!

reviews.text: ' 三哥醉拿手' = 醉豬手，好味 😍 麻辣醉雞，真係要食到辣才試。

掃食必到之處！
咖哩汁正！
臭豆腐正！
麵筋吸盡咖哩汁，掂啊！
位置略偏，主要做馬鞍山街坊生意！舖內裝修普通，D 櫈幾好坐，尚算乾淨企理！主打上海嘢，味道都唔錯！湯麵湯底清清哋，麵質爽滑，略嫌 D 餸少咗 D，菜飯份量略少，大男人會食唔飽，價錢對比份量來說，亦略貴些小！不過喺馬鞍山呢個美食沙漠嚟講，算係一個唔錯嘅選擇！！
麻辣夠麻，好此道者要試！
